00:03:43.458 --> 00:03:47.291
and culturally, and be in a position to craft this year’s work plan!

00:03:47.291 --> 00:03:49.458
Imagine that your director shares with you

00:03:49.458 --> 00:03:52.625
this coming year’s priorities for your directorate:

00:03:52.625 --> 00:03:55.125
protect aquatic ecosystems,

00:03:55.125 --> 00:03:59.500
sustain fisheries and manage the issuing of licenses.

00:03:59.500 --> 00:04:00.959
Using the dropdown menus,

00:04:00.959 --> 00:04:04.792
choose the best option for each section of this work plan.

00:04:07.792 --> 00:04:10.875
To help you wrap your mind around how to fill out the other sections

00:04:10.875 --> 00:04:14.542
of the work plan, let’s continue with the same scenario.

00:04:14.542 --> 00:04:15.667
Looking at your draft,

00:04:15.667 --> 00:04:19.333
you’ll notice that some items may have been dropped into the wrong location

00:04:19.333 --> 00:04:20.917
or may be missing.

00:04:20.917 --> 00:04:23.417
Update your draft accordingly.

00:04:28.417 --> 00:04:29.333
Alright.

00:04:29.333 --> 00:04:32.583
Your director tells you that they’ve been to a steering committee meeting

00:04:32.583 --> 00:04:35.250
and that they now have three new pieces of information

00:04:35.250 --> 00:04:38.000
that should be reflected in your work plan:

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:40.709
1) there will be new software implementation

00:04:40.709 --> 00:04:44.083
to speed up the issuing of licenses;

00:04:44.083 --> 00:04:49.542
2) there’s a new policy that now requires licenses to be issued in 15 days,

00:04:49.542 --> 00:04:53.001
not 30 days, starting on November 1st;

00:04:53.001 --> 00:04:58.375
and 3) there’s been a decision not to replace a retiring employee.

00:05:02.291 --> 00:05:05.417
Let’s take what you have learned into real life.

00:05:05.417 --> 00:05:08.917
Your organization will have their own ways of doing things.

00:05:08.917 --> 00:05:12.750
Take a time out from the course to scan your intranet

00:05:12.750 --> 00:05:14.917
and see which templates are used.

00:05:14.917 --> 00:05:18.291
Connect with your colleagues, your director, your financial officer

00:05:18.291 --> 00:05:20.834
to have a chat about work plans.

